               <p>Coming down Snow Hill, I lost my handkerchief, on the 9th of May, I felt the prisoner take my handkerchief, I turned round and took hold of him, and I saw him drop it out of his right hand, when I tried to stop him, he ran away, I cried stop thief.</p>
